  <Pages>
    <Page Name="Intro">
      <Text>You find yourself in a large room with yellow walls. You have a couple of options. You could:</Text>
      <Choice Target="WalkAround" Shortcut="1">Walk around aimlessly.</Choice>
      <Text>Alternatively, you could:</Text>
      <Choice Target="SitAround" Shortcut="2">Sit around boredly.</Choice>
      <Text>And, finally, you could:</Text>
      <Choice Target="Quit" Shortcut="3">Quit the game angrily.</Choice>
      <Text>The choice is yours.</Text>
    </Page>

    <Page Name="WalkAround">
      <Text>There's nothing here.</Text>
      <Choice Target="Intro" Shortcut="1">What to do next...</Choice>
    </Page>

    <Page Name="SitAround">
      <Text>You sit for a while.</Text>
      <Choice Target="Intro" Shortcut="1">What to do next...</Choice>
    </Page>

    <Page Name="Quit">
      <Text>A sensible decision!</Text>
      <Text>*You win!*</Text>
    </Page>
  </Pages>
